{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020/06/responsive-web-design-tech-review/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"J. Pedro Ribeiro"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3cffc672-9d0b-50cd-be39-afb564fe4b31","excerpt":"Over the past several months I've been working with Packt Publishing as a technical reviewer for their new release: Responsive Web Design with HTML5 and CSSâ€¦","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 451px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b2da3bdebe6c1c8ec896eb041968eb06/8f864/rwd-cover.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 110.75949367088609%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Responsive Web Design with HTML5 and CSS - Third Edition Book Cover\"\n        title=\"Responsive Web Design with HTML5 and CSS - Third Edition Book Cover\"\n        src=\"/static/b2da3bdebe6c1c8ec896eb041968eb06/8f864/rwd-cover.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b2da3bdebe6c1c8ec896eb041968eb06/81b7c/rwd-cover.webp 158w,\n/static/b2da3bdebe6c1c8ec896eb041968eb06/6ea66/rwd-cover.webp 315w,\n/static/b2da3bdebe6c1c8ec896eb041968eb06/8f864/rwd-cover.webp 451w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 451px) 100vw, 451px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Over the past several months I've been working with <a href=\"https://www.packtpub.com/\">Packt Publishing</a> as a technical reviewer for their new release: <a href=\"https://www.packtpub.com/gb/web-development/responsive-web-design-with-html5-and-css-third-edition\">Responsive Web Design with HTML5 and CSS - Third Edition</a>.</p>\n<p>I've previously <a href=\"/2015/07/being-technical-book-reviewer/\">shared my experience working as a tech reviewer</a>, in fact, I've reviewed their 1st edition back in 2015.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 410px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c336b64d579836a45e72e9e532d5f002/0cb6c/reviewer-screenshot.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.0506329113924%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRm4AAABXRUJQVlA4IGIAAADQAwCdASoUAA8APtFWo0uoJKMhsAgBABoJZQCdACKl2PF6TAPVBeIA4gbQPsCStSKFYUoHRHpeSeIJMusSHGp6I7w4+djPlodJrDbyJ/95Gb6bTwFaTaX7iE4LW5K7JcoAAA=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Snippet of the reviewer section\"\n        title=\"Snippet of the reviewer section\"\n        src=\"/static/c336b64d579836a45e72e9e532d5f002/0cb6c/reviewer-screenshot.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c336b64d579836a45e72e9e532d5f002/81b7c/reviewer-screenshot.webp 158w,\n/static/c336b64d579836a45e72e9e532d5f002/6ea66/reviewer-screenshot.webp 315w,\n/static/c336b64d579836a45e72e9e532d5f002/0cb6c/reviewer-screenshot.webp 410w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>This new edition is beautifully written by <a href=\"https://benfrain.com/\">Ben Frain</a>, in a very informal, joyful way. The kind of book I wish I had when I started my journey as a web developer.</p>\n<p>You can check out more about the book on the <a href=\"https://www.packtpub.com/gb/web-development/responsive-web-design-with-html5-and-css-third-edition\">Packt Pub website</a>.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Tech Review for Responsive Web Design 3rd Edition","date":"June 27, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020/06/responsive-web-design-tech-review/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/06/book-review-click/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Book Review: Click! - How to Encourage Clicks Without Shady Tricks","tags":["book review","conversion","business","strategy"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/10/quote-john-kenneth-galbraith/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Quote #4","tags":["quotes"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454","792910177"],"slicesMap":{}}